CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, August 10, 1957, pg. 17, reads: "Slums Growing in Homewood? - Repairs Needed - Members of the Homewood Comunity [sic] Improvement Association cite structures like these two concrete porches of the Rosedale St. apartment buildings shown as instances where immediate repairs are needed."
TitMainTitle: Facade of three-story brick multi-unit apartment buildings with dilapidated concrete porches, Rosedale Street, Homewood
